"Right about now... I need all eyes up front. ${b} is heading your way. Fellas, grab some cash — you're gonna need it. Here she comes... ${b}."
"Hold on, hold on... y'all ain't ready for this one. ${b} is about to shut this stage down. Paper up, boys. This is not a drill. Here she comes... ${b}."
"Listen up, my guys. You came here for the best, and the best is about to deliver. ${b}, coming to the main stage. Open those wallets wide. The beautiful ${b}."
"Who's got cash? I hope it's you, because ${b} is about to earn every single dollar. Main stage, right now. Get comfortable — and get generous. ${b}."
"Gentlemen... I need you to do me a favor. Put that phone down, pick that cash up. ${b} is about to take the stage and she deserves your full attention. The lovely ${b}."
"All eyes front, boys. No distractions. ${b} is heading to the main stage and she came to work tonight. Show her that paper. Coming up... ${b}."
"This next one's a problem, fellas — in the best way. ${b} about to hit the main stage. These ladies make their living off of what you're giving. Let's go... ${b}."
"Real talk, gentlemen. Some of y'all been sitting on that cash all night. Time to let it go. ${b} is coming to the stage. Open those wallets... the beautiful ${b}."
"Players... check this out. ${b} is about to grace the main stage. She didn't get all dressed up for nothing. Tip like you mean it. Here she comes... ${b}."
"Main stage alert, fellas. ${b} is in the building and she's heading your way. If you're close to the rail, you better have cash in hand. Don't be that guy. The one and only... ${b}."
"What's good, gentlemen. I got somebody special for you. ${b} is up next on the main stage. Trust me on this one — get your bread ready. Here she comes."
"Hey, hey, hey... main stage is about to get real interesting. ${b} is on her way out. She's worth every dollar, fellas. Open those wallets. ${b}."
"Big spenders, this one's for you. ${b} is about to show you why she's on this stage. Get those ones out, get up close. Show her some love... ${b}."
